TopicTitle: The mysterious object I found near Mun when playing version 1.12.4

Articles.Content:
I discovered this object at the tracking station while I was setting up the communications network for the Mun.

It was marked as an A-class asteroid, but when I controlled the detector to approach it, I found that it was a regular tetrahedron and flashed green.

The name it identifies in the tracking station is Ast.MQW-623 , but when I right click on it it says a name called Space Tetrahedron.

The surface looks smooth and has collision volumes. I let the detector hit it, but it didn't move.

After discussions between me and the experts in the group, we believe that he is the stinger in the Blueshift module.
